raw_text = "~ start
do Story.set_location(\"lecture_hall\")
Naomi: Morning there!
Player: Hi Naomi
Naomi: Sorry give me a moment
Naomi: Still waking up lol
Naomi: img: naomi/19
Player: At this time?
Naomi: I knoww! It's not like me is it haha
Naomi: Caleb pushed me to take a long break and...
Naomi: Maybe that's TMI, nevermind! 😇
- You can tell me 😉 [#redheart] [if Story.red_heart >= 2]
	set Story.red_heart += 1
	Player: You can tell me 😉
	Naomi: Hey someone's in a mood this morning 😏
	Naomi: I won't lie and tell you that I'm not in one 🤭
	Naomi: Caleb completely disarmed me last night 😳 hehe
	Naomi: img: naomi/20
	- No fair
		Player: No fair
		Naomi: Totally fair 😌
	- After all we've been through? [#redheart] [if Story.red_heart >= 3]
		Player: After all we've been through?
		Naomi: Jeez you're relentless 😂
		Naomi: But y'know.. I like that in a guy 😗
		Naomi: So here's a little something for you hehe
		Naomi: img: naomi/21
		Naomi: Don't stare too hard now or I'll have to complain to Mabel about this 😘
		Player: 🫠
		Naomi: I'm just teasing you
- Glad you were able to get some rest
	Player: Glad you were able to get some rest
	Naomi: Awwh thanks
	Naomi: I don't want it to become a habit tho lol
	Naomi: But that sweet boy was adamant last night 😃
Naomi: Anyway!
Naomi: Saturday.
Player: What's on Saturday?
Naomi: Me and you are gonna do a nude photoshoot together 🤭
- W-what?
	Player: W-what?
	Naomi: Shocker huh!
- H-huh!?
	Player: H-huh!?
	Naomi: Shocker huh!
- I like the sound of that 😎
